description: This was my crowd funding video for my second full length documentary about mentors and students, in this case, a 90 year old Master, Jimmy Heath, and a high school band of Jazz students at the Tucson Jazz Institute.   To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
